        <h1 class="page-title">Kandinsky's Color Theory</h1>
        <p class="page-description">
            Wassily Kandinsky, master form teacher at the Bauhaus (1922-1933), developed a revolutionary theory connecting geometric forms to primary colors. Experience this fundamental principle through interactive exploration.
        </p>
    </div>
